    <item>
      <title>Galaxy 的 Thorn 表示，比特币 ETF 期权将降低波动性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/bitcoin-etf-options-will-lower-volatility-galaxy-s-thorn-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Galaxy Digital 的亚历克斯·索恩 (Alex Thorn) 表示，领先规模 430 亿美元的 iShares 比特币信托基金 (iShares Bitcoin Trust) 领域的期权可用性可能会降低波动性并增加原始加密货币的投资者基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/bitcoin-etf-options-will-lower-volatility-galaxy-s-thorn-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 19:05:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的媒体公司正在洽谈收购 Bakkt 加密货币平台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/bakkt-surges-on-ft-report-of-sale-talks-with-trump-media</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的特朗普媒体科技集团公司正在就收购数字资产市场 Bakkt Holdings Inc. 进行谈判，这些知情人士不愿透露姓名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/bakkt-surges-on-ft-report-of-sale-talks-with-trump-media</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 21:13:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“华尔街鳄鱼”因加密货币案被判处 18 个月监禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/hacker-s-wife-razzlekhan-gets-18-months-for-money-laundering</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这位在说唱视频中自称“华尔街鳄鱼”和“Razzlekhan”的女子因帮助其黑客丈夫清洗从 Bitfinex 交易所窃取的加密货币而被判入狱 18 个月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/hacker-s-wife-razzlekhan-gets-18-months-for-money-laundering</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 18:58:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着加密资产上涨，纳斯达克准备上市现货比特币 ETF 期权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/nasdaq-poised-to-list-spot-bitcoin-etf-options-amid-crypto-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳斯达克公司计划于周二推出贝莱德公司比特币交易所交易基金的期权，允许投资者使用衍生品押注或做空全球最大的数字资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/nasdaq-poised-to-list-spot-bitcoin-etf-options-amid-crypto-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 18:16:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛准备分拆其数字资产平台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/goldman-readies-plans-to-spin-out-its-digital-assets-platform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团正在与潜在合作伙伴进行洽谈，计划将其数字资产平台分拆为一家新公司，供大型金融公司通过区块链技术创建、交易和结算金融工具。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/goldman-readies-plans-to-spin-out-its-digital-assets-platform</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币从美国大选以来代币最大跌幅中反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/bitcoin-btc-trades-near-90-000-after-largest-drop-since-us-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币在波动的交易中从美国大选以来最大的两天跌幅中恢复过来，这反映了人们对当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的政策议程影响的评估不断转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/bitcoin-btc-trades-near-90-000-after-largest-drop-since-us-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 01:09:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
